826
01:07:25.918 --> 01:07:27.544
Mr. Rozelle?

827
01:07:31.381 --> 01:07:33.217
No more pseudonyms. Cooper.

828
01:07:36.220 --> 01:07:37.804
No more running.

829
01:07:39.306 --> 01:07:40.807
