There's no getting out.

924
01:19:46.866 --> 01:19:49.410
- There's no getting out for me.
- Charlie.

925
01:19:50.536 --> 01:19:52.872
It wasn't supposed to be this way.

926
01:19:54.332 --> 01:19:56.459
It wasn't supposed to be
this difficult.

927
