they don't know how to handle your power.

954
01:21:51.199 --> 01:21:52.867
Here we can handle it.

955
01:21:54.535 --> 01:21:56.204
Because we made you.

956
01:22:00.083 --> 01:22:01.334
Look at your father.

957
