evacuate all non-military stafif

973
01:23:41.475 --> 01:23:43.769
Evacuate all non-military stafif

974
01:23:50.610 --> 01:23:53.196
evacuate all non-military stafif

975
01:24:00.036 --> 01:24:02.455
Evacuate all non-military stafif

976
